Package com.heretere.hdl.dependency.maven.annotation

Annotation Type MavenRepository

@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(TYPE)
@Repeatable(List.class)
public @interface MavenRepository
Used to define a maven repo url for the dependencies.
